  "remarks": "Semyon Pegov is a Russian military blogger and runs one of the most popular pro-war social media channels in Russia, WarGonzo. He frequently appears in Russian state controlled media. Semyon Pegov and WarGonzo spread anti-Ukrainian propaganda and promote the Russian military and PMC Wagner, depicting Ukrainian forces as Nazis and disseminating false information on NATO biological laboratories in Mariupol.",
